Nkosinathi Innocent Maphumulo, famously known as DJ Black Coffee as has bagged many awards, hangs out with the who's who of Hollywood and Beyonce loves his music. JOHANNESBURG - World-renowned DJ Black Coffee, real name Nkosinathi Innocent Maphumulo and actress and businesswoman, Mbali Enhle are allegedly heading for a split. Sunday World published an article saying Enhle has filed for divorce. She also took to Instagram on Sunday morning to address news reports and confirmed the matter was in court. READ: Black Coffee heads back to Vegas for residency She asked for space to deal with the divorce for “silence for the sake of her children.” Earlier this year, the were rumours that the couple's relationship was rocky. . A post shared by  Enhle Mbali Mlotshwa (@enhlembali_) on Nov 10, 2019 at 1:34am PST